How to Run The Tests within your directory
python3.6 -m unittest

How to run all tests in a specific Module?
python3.6 -m unittest tests.test_wealth_manger
or
python3.6 -m unittest tests.test_wealth_manger.py

How to run specific Test Case within a Module?
python3.6 -m unittest tests.test_wealth_manger.TestCalculate

How to run Specific method within a test case
python3.6 -m unittest tests.test_wealth_manger.TestCalculate.test_calculate_easy_first
